CREATE TABLE Sales
  (  
	SourceID int NOT NULL, 
	UniqueOrderID	varchar(64),
	OrderID	varchar(64),
	OrderDetailsID	varchar(64),
	UniqueMovieID	varchar(64),
	MovieID	varchar(64),
	Quantity	Integer,
	UnitCost	Float,
	LineNumber	Integer,
	CustomerID	varchar(64),
	UniqueCustomerID	varchar(64),
	OrderDate	Date,
	ShipDate	Date,
	TotalCost	Float
  )  
WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX);
